I Wezan ad teqbel?
Ala aqbal ara teqbel.
Yebda yuttuɣal-itt-id rruḥ.
Awal-agi n tmeddakelt-ines yuɣal-as d abeḥri di turet.
Imi ara fɣeɣ tura anda ara sɛeddiɣ iḍ-agi.
Temmeɣ tmeddakelt-ines ɣer uqrab-ines teddem-d azal n xemsa neɣ setta twerqtin.
Ax idrimen-agi ruḥ ṭṭef taxxamt deg usensu, ṣṣbeḥ ruh ɣer ttiɛad-inem di lawan.
